✅ Resource Group
✅ Virtual Network + Subnet
✅ Public IP
✅ Azure Load Balancer (Standard SKU)
✅ Backend Pool
✅ Health Probe
✅ LB Rule

Summary of What This Creates
Resource	Purpose
Resource Group ->	Container for resources
VNet + Subnet	-> Network for VMs
Public IP	-> Entry point
Load Balancer	-> Azure Standard LB
Backend Pool	-> Where VM NICs are added
Probe	-> Health monitoring
Rule	-> LB routing rule (80 → 80)
